DESCRIPTION:Bee vs. The Village is a stand-up comedy show about culture cla
 sh\, identity\, race\, and outsider life in a small German village. An Afri
 can American comedian shares sharp\, funny stories about marriage\, belongi
 ng\, village customs\, and the strange rules people expect you to follow wi
 thout ever saying them out loud. Warm\, biting\, and deeply relatable\, thi
 s is observational comedy for expats\, outsiders\, and anyone who has ever 
 tried to fit into a world that never quite fit them back.\nMore info: https
